show.description: Amid Diwali’s chaos, Aditi meets Sameer, a quiet, mysterious man living on the streets. When her life spirals after a brutal betrayal, Sameer steps in with a shocking offer—one that feels both dangerous and inevitable. But behind his worn clothes lies a secret far bigger than she imagines. As their worlds collide, buried truths, hidden enemies, and a shadowed past begin to surface. In this high-stakes game, trust is a risk—and love might be the trap.
